text.section:
The consumer members of the Board:
Shall be a member of the general public;
May not be or ever have been an optometrist or in training to become an optometrist;
May not have a household member who is an optometrist or in training to become an optometrist;
May not participate or ever have participated in a commercial or professional field related to optometry;
May not have a household member who participates in a commercial or professional field related to optometry; and
May not have had within 2 years before appointment a substantial financial interest in a person regulated by the Board.
